<plot>Geraldo Rivera, the "Skipper" begins an around the world journey with his family in this first of a six part series of hour-long adventures on his 'old ketch' "Voyager" to circumnavigate the world, ending up in Tonga on the International Date Line in time for New Years Eve celebrations. Later episodes are entitled, "Voyager: Geraldo Rivera". Aired with big ratings on the Travel Channel, a Discovery network.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?474009</url></doc>
